WEBVTT

00:00:00.844 --> 00:00:02.905
I used to have this recurring dream

00:00:02.929 --> 00:00:05.341
where I'd walk into a roomful of people,

00:00:06.388 --> 00:00:08.960
and I'd try not to make
eye contact with anyone.

00:00:10.220 --> 00:00:11.935
Until someone notices me,

00:00:11.959 --> 00:00:13.402
and I just panic.

00:00:14.213 --> 00:00:16.017
And the person walks up to me,

00:00:16.041 --> 00:00:18.550
and says, "Hi, my name is So-and-so.

00:00:18.574 --> 00:00:19.933
And what is your name?"

00:00:20.313 --> 00:00:23.498
And I'm just quiet, unable to respond.

00:00:25.196 --> 00:00:27.639
After some awkward silence, he goes,

00:00:27.663 --> 00:00:29.244
"Have you forgotten your name?"

00:00:29.851 --> 00:00:31.300
And I'm still quiet.